{"id":7226,"date":"2024-01-30T10:59:31","date_gmt":"2020-03-30T05:29:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=7226"},"modified":"2024-04-23T16:40:47","modified_gmt":"2024-04-23T11:10:47","slug":"modern-coffee-table","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/modern-coffee-table\/","title":{"rendered":"One Sip At A Time In Style: Modern Coffee Table Designs For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Your coffee table is the essence of your living room; it rests in the centre of your home is a piece of multifunctional furniture too<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A coffee table in a living room is usually an afterthought. But if you ask interior design experts it is actually that piece of furniture which anchors a space together.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern coffee table designs these days come with smart storage ideas, a pop-up work desk, and in myriad styles and materials. Coffee tables are not just a place to put up your feet and watch sitcoms! From practical to highly chic and everything in between, a coffee table can alter the look of your living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are our picks for coffee table designs, those that are stylish and efficient. Your coffee mugs and magazines will thank you for bringing one of these to your home. All you need to do now is pick your favourite one!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Nesting Coffee Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A modern nesting coffee table is an excellent decor hack if you live in a small home or studio apartment. This type has two tables, one slightly smaller than the other, that fits beneath each other as shown in this image. So when you need an extra table get one of these iron legged tables designed with a circular wooden top; they are durable and chic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014422\/modern-nesting-coffee-table.jpg\" alt=\"Modern nesting coffee tables home is an excellent decor hack if you live in a small house.\" class=\"wp-image-7235\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014422\/modern-nesting-coffee-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014422\/modern-nesting-coffee-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014422\/modern-nesting-coffee-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014422\/modern-nesting-coffee-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern White Coffee Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This white coffee table takes sophistication to a different level with its simplistic design. A simple round top white coffee table like this makes a great addition to your living room or a bedroom. Both these spaces usually have a lot of colour be it on the walls or upholstery so a simple coffee table brings in balance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014440\/white-modern-coffee-tables-home.jpg\" alt=\"White coffee table home decor takes sophistication to a different level with its simplistic design.\" class=\"wp-image-7239\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014440\/white-modern-coffee-tables-home.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014440\/white-modern-coffee-tables-home-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014440\/white-modern-coffee-tables-home-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014440\/white-modern-coffee-tables-home-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Coffee Table With Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There\u2019s never enough storage, isn\u2019t it? This coffee table not only offers storage space but also looks elegant in this living room. If you are a bookworm chances are your coffee table will be filled with a pile of books. This modern coffee table design gets you sorted. Now you can keep your bestsellers organised.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014408\/home-decor-coffee-table-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Home decor coffee table with storage, bookworm can store their books and not only offers storage space but also looks elegant.\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014408\/home-decor-coffee-table-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014408\/home-decor-coffee-table-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014408\/home-decor-coffee-table-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014408\/home-decor-coffee-table-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\"><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/diy-furniture-ideas\/\">DIY Furniture Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rustic Style Coffee Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The wood plank tabletop and iron legs make this rustic style coffee table highly durable and easy to maintain. And it brings in the very sought after country-style look to a space. Not to mention a perfect one to hold your hot coffee mug or your glass of wine as you drown into your latest book.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014426\/rustic-style-home-decor-coffee-table.jpg\" alt=\"Wood plank table top and iron legs make this rustic style coffee table home highly durable.\" class=\"wp-image-7236\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014426\/rustic-style-home-decor-coffee-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014426\/rustic-style-home-decor-coffee-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014426\/rustic-style-home-decor-coffee-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014426\/rustic-style-home-decor-coffee-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Wide Faceted Coffee Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here is a new jewel in the world of modern&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">interior design<\/a>. A wide faceted coffee table, like we see in this image, has a wide surface area for extra space. It narrows down slightly at the bottom, making it suitable for a home that\u2019s high on style and low on space. Here, a black finished coffee table is backed by an iron cage-like base making it a masterpiece that\u2019s made to last for years to come.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014445\/wide-faceted-coffee-table-home-decor.jpg\" alt=\"Wide faceted coffee tables home are suitable for a home that's high on style and low on space.\" class=\"wp-image-7240\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014445\/wide-faceted-coffee-table-home-decor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014445\/wide-faceted-coffee-table-home-decor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014445\/wide-faceted-coffee-table-home-decor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014445\/wide-faceted-coffee-table-home-decor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/double-sided-sofa\/\">Unique Double Sided Sofa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Living room interiors thoughtfully designed to create joyful family memories!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23155243\/living-room-interiors-thoughtfully-designed-create-joyful-family-memories.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Coffee Table With A Glass Top<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nothing sets the glam quotient like the luxurious shine of a coffee table with a glass top. This is exactly what this modern coffee table offers you. A rectangular shaped table, this one is great for large modern style homes. A black glass top brings in sleek decor to this living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014404\/glass-coffee-table-center-pieces-for-home.jpg\" alt=\"Glass coffee table centerpieces for home brings in sleek decor to this living room.\" class=\"wp-image-7231\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014404\/glass-coffee-table-center-pieces-for-home.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014404\/glass-coffee-table-center-pieces-for-home-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014404\/glass-coffee-table-center-pieces-for-home-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014404\/glass-coffee-table-center-pieces-for-home-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/modern-living-room-design-ideas\/\">10 Modern Living Room Design Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Dual Toned Coffee Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This dual-toned modern danish coffee table works great for a nuclear family or a couple whose home remains loyal to minimalism. As seen in this image, this wood and white coffee table with a round top brings in a cool vibe to this space and blends in well the overall theme.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014356\/dual-toned-home-decorators-coffee-table.jpg\" alt=\"Home decorators coffee table with minimalistic dual-toned design.\" class=\"wp-image-7229\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014356\/dual-toned-home-decorators-coffee-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014356\/dual-toned-home-decorators-coffee-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014356\/dual-toned-home-decorators-coffee-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014356\/dual-toned-home-decorators-coffee-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Square Top Coffee Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This all-wood coffee table is a classic way to add a traditional touch to your modern space. The height of this coffee table is just right to serve its purpose; it\u2019s at easy reach to everyone sitting around. You can place your mug or books without stretching out too far. It has a shelf right beneath to neatly organise your books and magazines.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014435\/square-top-coffee-table.jpg\" alt=\"Coffee tables home with the square top design is an ideal way to add a traditional touch to your modern space.\" class=\"wp-image-7238\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014435\/square-top-coffee-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014435\/square-top-coffee-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014435\/square-top-coffee-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014435\/square-top-coffee-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And there, coffee tables that are more than just tables. Think about all the decor you would like to place on it, the colour scheme that appeals to you, and where you want to bring in these masterpieces before choosing one that\u2019s right one for you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-design-trends\/\">Living Room Design Trends<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Dreamy Interiors That Spell 'WOW'<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our design experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.